  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1641520/extras/973073a2bad779b9b30b9ead71f02bb9.webp?t=1640264043\" width=612 height=50 /></span><br>Survive among wild animals in hunger, thirst and harsh night conditions.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1641520/extras/d7482a40f7333d41435bc53badd60f4e.webp?t=1640264043\" width=612 height=50 /></span><br>Survive the wild world with <strong>7 different unique tool</strong> and <strong>14 different weapons</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1641520/extras/0325c6be6225d46638d1fb059b14af5b.webp?t=1640264043\" width=612 height=50 /></span><br>Make clothes for yourself with the items you collect from the forest and the skins of the animals you hunt.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1641520/extras/b99e5c80b63af64b0e61d0aaa305482d.webp?t=1640264043\" width=612 height=50 /></span><br>Build the house of your dreams with your collect from the forest. (Dynamic modular base building system is supported.)<br>Craft your furnace, campfire, storage box, standing torches, stonewall, bed and to be survive.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1641520/extras/44dd2f5e1905e18da43a144a19fc0a2f.webp?t=1640264043\" width=612 height=50 /></span><br>Build and manage your farm with water management and plant growth cycles.<br>(New plant and fruit species will be added.)<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1641520/extras/cba8ba612a7020a92f4d4b7f8cb16914.webp?t=1640264043\" width=612 height=50 /></span><br>Explore the jungle and fight with <strong>4 passive</strong> and <strong>3 active</strong> animals.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Development Roadmap</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Combat Mechanics   <br></li><li>New Furnitures<br></li><li>New Building Types<br></li><li>Complex Farming Mechanics (New Seeds)<br></li><li>Smooth Day & Night Cycle<br></li><li>New Islands<br></li><li>Water Vehicles (Raft, Boat)<br></li><li>Underwater Design<br></li><li>Multiple Language<br></li><li>Item Stack (Inventory System)<br></li><li>Steam Achievements</li></ul>",
